{"word":"G1878 - ἐπαναμιμνήσκω - epanamimnḗskō - ep-an-ah-mim-nace'-ko - Put in mind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπαναμιμνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epanamimnḗskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-an-ah-mim-nace'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Put in mind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஞாபகப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to recall to mind again"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G363 - ἀναμιμνήσκω - anamimnḗskō - an-am-im-nace'-ko/363\">G363</a>; to <i>remind of:</i> - put in mind.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}